com.upsight.android.logger

Interface UpsightLogger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Logger

    public interface UpsightLogger
    A logger implementation that collects logs as analytics data. All logs entries matching the log level set with this logger will be tracked as analytics data and become available to the developer.
    Note: These logs can contain sensitive information, hence it is important to carefully decide what to log with this class. Another important factor is the volume of logs that can be generated may impact the amount of analytics data being sent upstream potentially affecting your application's network usage.
    It is only recommended to use this logger for critical errors that may occur which you might collect analytics from.
